snippet.title: Rav Dror
snippet.description:
Rav Dror Moshe Cassouto brings us rare honest pure principles of truth that touch the heart of anyone who listens to his inspirational words. Our hope is that these inspirational videos will bring you closer to The Creator and inspire and motivate you to find your connection to Truth with joy, faith, and trust. The classes are based mostly on finding your inner truth, with a strong emphasis on personal prayer,  and faith.
